textline.data: the system shall save the recorded values
in a fifo inside flash memory in a section
by turn on Led with alarm
The System shall check if the pressure
is below a predefined threshold = 20 bar
The system shall store the pressure values
the system shall inform the crew
when the cabin has too high pressure
the high pressure in the cabin
